<p align="center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200814/a9366e3e080743a48480411a7b60447b.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">王斌银摄</p>
<p align="center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20200814/345e1ba816ff402d9afb2abe52b00849.jpeg" /></p>
<p align="center">王斌银 摄</p>
